<section class="pt-32 pb-16 px-6 md:px-12"><div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto"><h1 class="text-4xl font-black tracking-tighter mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1><div class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed space-y-4"><p>Flake & Flake Attorneys at Law respects your privacy. This policy describes how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.</p><p><strong class="text-white">Information We Collect:</strong> Name, email, phone number, and case details submitted through our website forms.</p><p><strong class="text-white">How We Use It:</strong> To respond to your inquiries, evaluate potential cases, and communicate with you about legal matters.</p><p><strong class="text-white">We Do Not:</strong> Sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes.</p><p><strong class="text-white">Security:</strong> We use reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access.</p><p><strong class="text-white">Contact:</strong> Questions about this policy? Call (702) 818-1800 or email jordan@flakeandflake.com.</p><p class="text-xs">Last updated: March 2026</p></div></div></section>
